text.section:
The consumer member of the Committee:
Shall be a member of the general public;
May not be or ever have been:
An electrologist;
A health care professional; or
In training to be an electrologist or a health care professional;
May not have a household member who is an electrologist, a health care professional, in training to be an electrologist, or in training to be a health care professional; and
May not:
Participate or ever have participated in a commercial or professional field related to electrology;
Have a household member who participates in a commercial or professional field related to electrology; or
Have, or have had within 2 years before appointment, a substantial financial interest in a person regulated by the Board.
